Interface IReceiptBulkImport

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IBulkImport
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IReceiptManager
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ReceiptManager

    public interface IReceiptBulkImport
extends IBulkImport
    IReceiptBulkImport interface for supporting uploading document records from XLS/JSON files into ParamNetwork.

    Using this interface you can import/read the file from different sources and import into ParamNetwork

    IReceiptBulkImport defines below categories of operations:

    • updateRecords will add records for a given config.

    • updateRecords will update records for a given config.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jitendra Kumar Balla, ParamNetwork

    • Method Detail

      • addRecords

        void addRecords(IReceiptBulkFileImportConfig uploadConfig)
         throws InvalidConfigException,
                FileNotFoundException,
                NetworkException,
                AccessDeniedException
        Method import all the documents from external file source to ParamNetwork.

        #addRecords(IReceiptBulkFileUploadConfig) <i>addRecords</i> method will read the file stream, then it will validate below items

        • Original file size with Steam bytes size
        • Validate file format with Param prescribed format
        • Record mandatory fields.
        If everything is valid, then it will add new record to param network, Otherwise it will throw an error.
        Parameters:
        uploadConfig - Upload config like, getFileContent(),File name,size, etc..,
        Throws:
        InvalidConfigException - If any file format is wrong then it will throw InvalidConfigException
        FileNotFoundException - Unable to read the content from the stream, then it will throw FileNotFoundException
        NetworkException - Unable to connect to ParamNode it will throw exception.
        AccessDeniedException - Not having enough access rights then it will thorw an error

      • updateRecords

        void updateRecords(IReceiptBulkFileImportConfig uploadConfig)
            throws InvalidConfigException,
                   FileNotFoundException,
                   NetworkException,
                   AccessDeniedException
        Method update all the documents from external file source to ParamNetwork.

        #updateRecords(IReceiptBulkFileUploadConfig) <i>updateRecords</i> method will read the file stream, then it will validate below items

        • Original file size with Steam bytes size
        • Validate file format with Param prescribed format
        • Record mandatory fields.
        • Record exists in the param network and having enough updates rights
        If everything is valid, then it will update record to param network, Otherwise it will throw an error.
        Parameters:
        uploadConfig - Upload config like, getFileContent(),File name,size, etc..,
        Throws:
        InvalidConfigException - If any file format is wrong then it will throw InvalidConfigException
        FileNotFoundException - Unable to read the content from the stream, then it will throw FileNotFoundException
        NetworkException - Unable to connect to ParamNode it will throw exception.
        AccessDeniedException - Not having enough access rights then it will thorw an error
